BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 571 Td (TACTICAL BREATHING \(Box Breathing - adapted from combat breathing\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 553 Td (1. Inhale through nose: 4 counts \(like taking cover\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 538 Td (2. Hold: 4 counts \(steady your position\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 523 Td (3. Exhale through mouth: 4 counts \(controlled release\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 508 Td (4. Hold empty: 4 counts \(reset\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 493 Td (Repeat 4-6 cycles. This activates your parasympathetic nervous system.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 465 Td (ORIENTING TO SAFETY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 447 Td (1. Slowly look around the room. Name what you see out loud.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 432 Td (2. Identify evidence of safety: locked doors, familiar objects, time/date.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 417 Td (3. Say: 'I am [name]. I am in [place]. It is [year]. I am safe.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 402 Td (4. Feel your feet on the ground. Press your back into the chair.) Tj ET
